    • Orders

      public Orders(String state, String paystate, Waiters waiterid, Users userid, String timeplaced, Integer tablenumber, KitchenStaff kitchenStaffId, Float price)
      This constructor builds an order with all its characteristics.
      Parameters:
      state - The state the order is in
      waiterid - The ID of the waiter that the order is assigned to
      userid - The ID of the user that placed the order
      timeplaced - The time the user placed the order
      tablenumber - The table number of the user
      price - The price of the order
